A romantic courtyard, hidden inside a variety of aromatic plants leads us to the interior.
“Villa il Vecchio Cortille - bouganville ” is fully equipped to meet all your needs (Wi-Fi, satellite TV, kitchen, laundry, etc.) while the welcoming reception of the owners will make your stay an unforgettable experience.
It is ideally located, very close to the Medieval Town, the "new marina", the port, supermarket, restaurants and bars.

Great place for a visit to Rhodes Town. Away from the busy old town but still easily walkable to all the sights. The property is beautifully presented, has all you need and lots of nice touches.
We were recommended to try the local restaurant 4 Rodies and we were glad we did. The food was incredible!

Stayed about a week
We had an amazing holiday at this Airbnb, it was in an ideal location, just a short walk from the old town. It has a private court yard which was a lovely space as well as a balcony, there were so many amazing great touches, including the fridge and cupboards stocked with some essentials, regular fresh towels and cleaning (which is unusual in most Airbnb’s we’ve stayed in). Comfortable bed, great host and mimosa was really friendly and helpful. Thank you for a wonderful holiday.
